<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="font-mono text-accent text-sm mb-2">01. About</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-heading mb-8">
        Who I am
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I'm a software developer and team lead based in Orlando, Florida, with
          close to a decade building production systems in the <strong class="text-text-heading">.NET ecosystem</strong>.
          I currently lead a development team at Voice Systems Engineering, where I
          architect and ship software that handles real-world voice and communications infrastructure.
        </p>
        <p>
          My path into tech wasn't linear — I started in economics, spent three years
          working Emirates business class in Dubai, then made a deliberate pivot into
          software engineering. That unconventional route gave me something most
          developers don't have: <strong class="text-text-heading">business acumen, global perspective,
          and the ability to communicate across disciplines</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          I hold a Master's in Computer Software Engineering, multiple Microsoft
          certifications, and a Mensa membership. I care about clean architecture,
          mentoring junior developers, and building systems that last.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-accent mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">Quick stats</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-text-muted">Experience</span>
              <span class="text-text-heading font-semibold">~8 years</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-text-muted">Current role</span>
              <span class="text-text-heading font-semibold">Team Lead</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-text-muted">Location</span>
              <span class="text-text-heading font-semibold">Orlando, FL</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-text-muted">Languages</span>
              <span class="text-text-heading font-semibold">EN / SR</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-accent mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">Certifications</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted">
            <li>MCPS: Microsoft Certified Professional</li>
            <li>MS: Programming in C#</li>
            <li>Systems Deployment Engineer</li>
            <li>Mensa Member</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
